verbs.description: [V: Has] liberal Hollywood just completely run out of original material ? Season four of Netflix ’s Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt , a ditzy , nonsensical comedy series , makes me think so . The first six episodes released on May 30 are randomly sprinkled with snide comments against President Trump and conservatives in general , and even beats the dead horse of white privilege .
